Question: Finding the common elements between N lists in Java: :I need to write a Java program that finds the intersection (common elements) of an arbitrary number of lists or arrays of integers (of arbitrary length). I guess that Java Lists may have a useful method in order to achieve this, but I am taking a look at the API and can´t find it.Any hint?
